title: Maracatu
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Organic, Western, Beer/Wine, Caribbean, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. All vegetarian except for fish. Uses many organic and local ingredients. Lentil veggie burger on whole wheat, falafel with hummus in pita, green salads, eggplant fajitas, past, gallo pinto, and more. World music played at night.
streetAddress: Main Road, front of La Plaza Futbol, Dominical
